"может занижать скорость из-за нехватки мощности."
msgstr ""
"Removes internet “stalls” when someone downloads or saturates the link "
"(video calls and games stop lagging). It caps the speed slightly below "
"the real one so the router manages the packet queue. It's demanding on "
"router performance: on high-speed plans (500+ Mbps) it may underrate the "
"speed due to lack of power."

#: src/re_sputnik/ui/advanced_screen.py:844
msgid "WAN-интерфейс (что ограничиваем)"
msgstr "WAN interface (what we limit)"

#: src/re_sputnik/ui/advanced_screen.py:845
msgid ""
"Устройство, через которое роутер выходит в интернет. Обычно определяется "
"автоматически."
msgstr ""
"The interface through which the router reaches the internet. Usually "
"detected automatically."

